INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (192, '新闻', 1, 'com.linq.web.controller.news.LinkNewsController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '', '/news/news', '127.0.0.1', ' 本机地址', '{\"newsContent\":\"<div class=\\\"videoPlayerWrap\\\">\\n<div data-reactroot=\\\"\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"video-title\\\"><a href=\\\"http://v.qq.com/x/page/n3110zs4x6r.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">杨幂身穿粉色旗袍搭配双马尾造型，尽显凹凸身材，不愧是我们的时尚达人</a>\\n<div class=\\\"autoPlay\\\">自动播放\\n<div class=\\\"atuobar enable\\\">&nbsp;</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"vn3110zs4x6r_wrap\\\" class=\\\"videoPlayer\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"videoPlayerMini\\\" draggable=\\\"true\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"vn3110zs4x6r\\\">\\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\\n<a class=\\\"txp_ad_more\\\" data-role=\\\"adplayer-video-detail-btn\\\">详情点击</a>广告剩余:&nbsp;9秒01:01</div>\\n<div class=\\\"player-float-head\\\">\\n<h4 class=\\\"float-title\\\">&nbsp;</h4>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\">7月5日，杨幂现身长沙录制《密室大逃脱》，一身粉红色旗袍造型，十分美艳。</p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\"><img class=\\\"content-picture\\\" src=\\\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12039506743/1000\\\" /></p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\">为了搭配这一套可爱的旗袍，杨幂扎起双马尾，戴着粉红色的&ldquo;桃子&rdquo;耳环，整体感觉既甜美又不失性感。</p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\">杨幂拥有圈中少见的好身材，不但前夫刘恺威知道，很多关注她的网友都一清二楚。</p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\"><img class=\\\"content-picture\\\" src=\\\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12039508761/1000\\\" /></p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\"><img class=\\\"content-picture\\\" src=\\\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12039508816/1000\\\" /></p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\">今天，这套粉红色的短旗袍，让她的A4腰成为镜头焦点，腰部以及小腹没有一丝赘肉，实在令人羡慕。</p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\"><img class=\\\"content-picture\\\" src=\\\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12039511990/1000\\\" /></p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\">杨幂这样的身材应该是天生的，全靠父母遗传的好基因，即使她后天不做运动都比一般人要苗条，更何况她作为明星平时少吃多餐，坚持锻炼身体，身材自然优胜于普通女性。</p>\\n<p class=\\\"one-p\\\"><img class=\\\"content-picture\\\" src=\\\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12039527153/1000\\\